SUMMARY:AI Workspace Training – Session 5: Memory Strategies for AI Agents
DESCRIPTION:AI Workspace Training Program — Session 5 of 11\n\nPresented by: Patricio Perez\, Tech Lead — Node Backend Team\n\n📋 THIS SESSION\nSession 5: Memory Strategies for AI Agents (Technical · 60 min)\n• The memory problem: Claude forgets between sessions\n• How embeddings work: text → vector → similarity search\n• Qdrant vector database and the embedding pipeline\n• Three search modes: semantic\, hybrid\, tiered\n• Knowledge graph: entity extraction and session relationships\n• Tiered memory architecture (Working → Episodic → Semantic → Resource)\n• Homework: Embed sessions\, search them\n\n📊 Attendance is tracked for each session (billing purposes).\n\n📊 COURSE SLIDES\n• Live (animated): https://patricioperezbla.github.io/ai-workspace-training/\n• PDF download: https://patricioperezbla.github.io/ai-workspace-training/ai-workspace-training_v10.pdf
